snippet.title: Tales of Phantasia SNES Opening
snippet.description: This is the opening sequence to the SNES version of Tales of Phantasia. It's an RPG by Namco. It has re-releases for Game Boy Advance, Sony Playstation and Sony PSP. For us hardcore fans, the SNES version will always have a place in our heart. The SNES version was only released in Japan but devote fans unofficially translated the whole game to English. If you wish to download a high quality version of this movie clip or download the game, then go to my site... http://www.fantasyanime.com
